com.locuslabs.sdk.maps.model

Class Marker.Options

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.locuslabs.sdk.maps.model.Marker.Options
  • Enclosing interface:
    Marker

    public static class Marker.Options
extends java.lang.Object
    Options Required: position - where to place the marker map - to contain the marker And one of: icon - an Icon object specifying icon parameters symbol - a Symbol object specifying symbol parameters Optional: clickable - whether or not this marker will generate click events draggable - whether or not this marker is draggable opacity - the opacity of the marker, from 0.0 to 1.0. visible - whether or not the marker is visible zIndex - the z-index of the marker floor - the floor on which the marker is drawn
